 been a bright spot in the challenged portfolio, more profitable and bigger=
 than when it was bought, per a source familiar.</p><p style=3D"margin:0;ma=
rgin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">But AT=
TN isn=E2=80=99t as core to the current Candle thesis as <strong>Reese With=
erspoon</strong>=E2=80=99s Hello Sunshine and its other production entities=
=E2=80=94Exile, Faraway Road, and Candle True Stories, all of which have
been consolidated under Hello Sunshine C.E.O. <strong>Sarah Harden</strong>=
=2E Candle also owns <em>Cocomelon</em>=
 studio Moonbug Entertainment, which o=
perates separately. Are those two units also for sale? A Candle rep says no=
, but a separate bank, Moelis &amp; Co., is still advising on potential M&a=
mp;A deals on the studio side. And now Raine is out pitching ATTN in the pu=
blishing and creative agency world.</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0=
px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;">It=E2=80=99s gonna be interesting to =
see how the merger dance plays out among all these independent, privately b=
acked producers that were conceived (and valued) on pre-correction models. =
I could see Moonbug selling to Disney or a rival, and the studio group coul=
d roll into Legendary or another general-interest player=E2=80=94though pro=
bably not for anything near that $900 million valuation that Candle put on =
Hello Sunshine back in 2021.</p></div>
