nd] once a film is finished, it is not unusual for a star to recut it. We d=
id a movie with an Oscar-winning director and the star did their own cut, w=
hich was better. The studio agreed, as did the director and the preview aud=
ience. Best cut wins.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=94<em>A producer</em></p><p style=3D"=
